# OS
.DS_Store

# Personal coaching data — contains sensitive data: storybank, scores, interview targets,
# compensation strategy, recruiter feedback, transcript excerpts, and personal reflections.
# Never commit this file. See README "Data and Privacy" section for details.
coaching_state.md

# Archive of closed interview loops: same sensitivity as coaching_state.md.
# Full loop details preserved here when loops are compressed in the main state file.
coaching_state_archive.md

# Active skill file (created by copying SKILL.md during setup)
CLAUDE.md

# Personal pipeline tracking — contains company names, stages, and interview outcomes
state/

# Application answer drafts — contains company-specific answers and story selections
job-search/

# Auto-generated by skills ecosystem (npx skills add) — machine-specific
.agents/
.claude/skills/
skills-lock.json
